    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Steam Next Fest Demo only includes early versions of Local Mode and Streamer Mode.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110320/extras/df6142dd19ca920a82d9eb25296dcffb.poster.avif?t=1749149540\" width=800 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110320/extras/df6142dd19ca920a82d9eb25296dcffb.webm?t=1749149540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Impostor is a unique social deception game, where you play either as an impostor, pretending to be an AI, or as the detective, who is trying to expose the impostor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The detective picks a question for the impostor to answer. The impostor must write an answer which will sound like it is AI-written. The impostor loses the round if he is exposed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110320/extras/4897c46b39ac5c00b538cb858975543b.gif?t=1749149540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110320/extras/4897c46b39ac5c00b538cb858975543b.poster.avif?t=1749149540\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are several game modes, each of which puts a new spin on this system.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Campaign Mode -</strong> Hone your human-detection skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online Mode -</strong> Play with other friends who own the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local Mode -</strong> Play locally on one computer, taking turns.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Streamer Mode -</strong> Play with your stream chat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110320/extras/3b77b9577572feb8d77994f6a1c3863a.poster.avif?t=1749149540\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110320/extras/3b77b9577572feb8d77994f6a1c3863a.webm?t=1749149540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is currently in the process of being tested and built in public, and should be ready around March.</p>",
